Can someone re-open this issue to make it visible? @c-w 

I changed [this line of annotation.css](https://github.com/doccano/doccano/blob/master/app/server/static/assets/css/annotation.css#L164), and it works like a charm. 

```
 .content .text-sequence {
-  white-space: normal; /* Not render newlines for sequence labelling */
-  height: auto;
+  white-space: pre-wrap;
 }
```
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8426290/78094282-08964100-7389-11ea-830b-735ebee0b112.png)

I see no undesirable side effects. Why not just fix it?
